(1, 'Bags', 'bags', 'blog', 'Explore the world of bags, from trendy totes to functional backpacks. Discover tips for choosing the perfect bag for any occasion, stylish recommendations, and how to care for your collection. Whether you’re a fashionista or a practical shopper, find insights to match your needs and elevate your style.', 1, 1, '2024-09-04 05:27:39', '2024-09-04 05:27:39', NULL),
(2, 'Fashion', 'fashion', 'blog', 'Fashion refers to the prevailing style or trend in clothing, accessories, footwear, makeup, and hairstyling that is popular at a particular time and place. It\'s a dynamic and ever-evolving aspect of culture that reflects social, economic, and cultural influences', 1, 1, '2024-09-04 05:28:14', '2024-09-04 05:28:14', NULL),
(3, 'Gym', 'gym', 'blog', 'Embark on a transformative journey with our gym-focused blog! Discover expert tips for maximizing workouts, insightful nutrition advice, and motivational stories to fuel your fitness journey. From beginners to seasoned athletes, explore a wealth of content tailored to sculpting a healthier, stronger you. Let\'s conquer those fitness goals together!', 1, 1, '2024-09-04 05:28:35', '2024-09-04 05:28:35', NULL),
(4, 'Yoga', 'yoga', 'blog', 'Embark on a journey of self-discovery and holistic wellness through the ancient practice of yoga. Dive into a world where mind, body, and spirit unite in harmony. From dynamic flows to serene meditation, explore the transformative power of yoga and unlock a path to inner peace and vibrant health.', 1, 1, '2024-09-04 05:29:04', '2024-09-04 05:29:04', NULL),
(5, 'Groceries', 'groceries', 'blog', 'Groceries and staples are the foundation of a well-stocked kitchen, encompassing essential food items that form the basis of meals. This category includes non-perishable items like rice, pasta, flour, oils, canned goods, and spices. Staples provide the building blocks for a wide range of recipes, allowing for diverse culinary creations. Careful grocery planning ensures a pantry stocked with nutritious and versatile options, enabling efficient meal preparation while accommodating individual dietary preferences.', 1, 1, '2024-09-04 05:29:55', '2024-09-04 05:29:55', NULL),
(6, 'Top Authors', 'top-authors', 'blog', 'Popular and highly-regarded writers known for their bestselling books and impactful stories.', 1, 1, '2024-09-04 05:31:41', '2024-09-04 05:31:41', NULL),
(7, 'Top Creators', 'top-creators', 'blog', 'Leading content makers who produce engaging, original content and have a large, dedicated audience across platforms.', 1, 1, '2024-09-04 05:31:55', '2024-09-04 05:31:55', NULL),
(8, 'Christmas', 'christmas', 'blog', 'Discover the magic of Christmas with our festive blog! From decorating tips and gift ideas to heartwarming traditions and delicious recipes, we cover everything you need to make this holiday season unforgettable. Embrace the joy, love, and spirit of Christmas with us!', 1, 1, '2024-10-04 06:06:37', '2024-10-04 06:06:37', NULL),
(9, 'Jewellery', 'jewellery', 'blog', 'Discover the allure of exquisite craftsmanship and timeless elegance with our captivating journey into the world of jewellery. From sparkling diamonds to lustrous pearls, delve into the artistry, history, and significance behind each piece, and unlock the secrets of adornment that have fascinated humanity for centuries.', 1, 1, '2024-10-04 06:07:21', '2024-10-04 06:07:21', NULL),
(10, 'Flowers', 'flowers', 'blog', 'Explore the vibrant world of flowers, where beauty blooms in every petal. From the delicate elegance of roses to the cheerful exuberance of sunflowers, discover the language of flowers and their significance in cultures worldwide. Let their colors and fragrances inspire and uplift your spirit.', 1, 1, '2024-10-04 06:08:02', '2024-10-04 06:08:02', NULL),
(11, 'Books', 'books', 'blog', 'Delve into the captivating world of literature with our blog on books. From timeless classics to contemporary page-turners, we explore the magic of storytelling, offer insightful reviews, and share recommendations across genres. Let\'s embark on a journey through the boundless realms of imagination that books offer.', 1, 1, '2024-10-04 06:08:36', '2024-10-04 06:08:36', NULL),
(12, 'Watches', 'watches', 'blog', 'Explore the timeless world of watches! From classic elegance to cutting-edge innovation, our blog delves into the intricate craftsmanship, iconic designs, and latest trends in horology. Discover the perfect timepiece for every occasion, unravel the stories behind renowned brands, and embark on a journey through the fascinating history of watches.', 1, 1, '2024-10-04 06:09:29', '2024-10-04 06:09:29', NULL),
(13, 'Footwear', 'footwear', 'blog', 'Explore the world of footwear, where fashion meets function. From classic kicks to cutting-edge designs, discover the perfect pair to elevate any ensemble. Whether you\'re strolling the streets or strutting the runway, step into style with our curated collection of footwear trends, tips, and must-have staples.', 1, 1, '2024-10-04 06:09:51', '2024-10-04 06:09:51', NULL),
(14, 'Medical Products', 'medical-products', 'blog', 'Explore the latest advancements and essentials in medical products, from cutting-edge devices to everyday necessities. Uncover insights into innovations enhancing patient care, managing health conditions, and improving medical practices. Stay informed about the diverse range of tools and technologies shaping the landscape of healthcare delivery and wellness.', 1, 1, '2024-10-04 06:10:16', '2024-10-04 06:10:16', NULL),
(15, 'Farm Fresh Produce', 'farm-fresh-produce', 'blog', 'Indulge in the vibrant flavors of farm-fresh produce with our enticing array of fruits and vegetables straight from the source. Discover the essence of freshness as we delve into the journey from soil to table, celebrating nature\'s bounty and the wholesome goodness it brings to your plate.', 1, 1, '2024-10-04 06:10:43', '2024-10-04 06:10:43', NULL),
(16, 'Furnishing', 'furnishing', 'blog', 'Furniture encompasses a wide range of functional and decorative items designed to enhance living and working spaces. It includes various pieces that serve practical purposes while contributing to the overall aesthetics and ambiance of a room or environment. Furniture is an essential aspect of interior design and plays a crucial role in creating comfortable and functional living, working, and recreational spaces.', 1, 1, '2024-10-04 06:11:13', '2024-10-04 06:11:13', NULL),
(17, 'Marijuana', 'marijuana', 'blog', 'Explore the world of marijuana, from its history as a medicinal and recreational plant to its modern-day legal status and uses. Learn about the science behind its effects, the cultural significance it holds, and the ongoing debates surrounding its legalization and impact on society.', 1, 1, '2024-10-04 07:01:15', '2024-10-04 07:01:15', NULL),
(18, 'Nursery', 'nursery', 'blog', 'Nestled in the heart of our blog is a lush haven, where seeds of curiosity blossom into vibrant stories. Explore the nurturing world of nurseries, where greenery meets growth. From plant care tips to botanical beauty, our nurturing articles will cultivate your passion for all things green.', 1, 1, '2024-10-04 23:37:27', '2024-10-04 23:37:27', NULL),
(19, 'Cosmetics', 'cosmetics', 'blog', 'Explore the world of cosmetics where beauty meets science and artistry. From skincare essentials to glamorous makeup trends, uncover the secrets behind flawless looks. Dive into product reviews, tutorials, and expert tips to enhance your natural beauty and express your unique style through the transformative power of cosmetics.', 1, 1, '2024-10-04 23:52:46', '2024-10-04 23:52:46', NULL);
